AJ,

To build PSI4 on blueridge, I'm using a boost library and python that I
compiled in my own area.  Here's my setup:

./setup --prefix=$HOME/psi4 --cc=icc --cxx=icpc --fc=ifort
--boost-incdir=~crawdad/boost/include --boost-libdir=~crawdad/boost/lib
--python=~crawdad/bin/python --type=release build

See if that works for you.  If should not need to build the boost library
distributed with PSI4.

-TDC
--
Prof. T. Daniel Crawford
crawdad@vt.edu

